quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  20,13,"Min Mi SuЙ“ike ma -an Muusaa- fii yottinngol Nulal an ngal, heЙ—o ko Mi woni Wahayinnde kon e maaЙ—a."
  20,14,"Pellet, ko Min woni Alla reweteeЙ—o e goonga alaa tanaa Am, Rewam Min Tun tottir Julde nden e noone Й“urЙ—o timmude fii yo a annditam e nder mayre."
  20,15,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko arayngal feere alaa ngal hewtay, MiЙ—o Й—aЙ“a suuЙ—ude ngal TagaaЙ—o woo anndaa nde ngal waЙ—ata, kono hiЙ“e anndira maa- ndeeji maggal sabu ko NulaaЙ—o on humpitiЙ“e kon; fii yo yoЙ“e kala wonkii ko ki golli kon, si tawii ko ko moЖґЖґi maaЙ—um si ko ko bone."
  20,16,"Wata martine(firlitma) e goonginngol ngal e heblanorgol golle moЖґЖґe Й—en, on mo gomЙ—inaa ngal immorde e yedduЙ“e Й“en, o jokki ko welata wonkii makko kin immorde e harminaaЙ—i Й—in, o halkori sabu Й—um."
  20,17,"Ko woni nden huunde wonunde ka Г±aamo maaЙ—a an Muusaa?"
  20,18,"Muusaa (yo o his) maaki: "Ndun ko tuggordu am; miЙ—o tuggoo ndu ka yaadu, miЙ—o woppira ndu leЙ—Й—e Й—en fii yo kaaki majje Й—in saaman dammi am Й—in, miЙ—o mari nafa kadi e mayru hara wanaa koo ko mi jaЕ‹tii"."
  20,19,"Alla Daali: "LiЙ“u ndu, an Muusaa"."
  20,20,"Muusaa liЙ“i ndu, ndu waylii mboddi hindi yaha e yaccaade."
  20,21,"Alla Daalani Muusaa (yo o his): "nanngu tuggordu ndun, wota a hulu immorde e waylagol mayru mboddi, aray Men rutta ndu si nanngii ndu faade e noone mayru arano on."
  20,22,"WaЙ—u junngo maaЙ—a ngon ka nder jiiba maa; ngo yaltay ko ngo rawnungo hara ngo colЙ—aa(ngo wonddani e baras), Й—um ko maande Й—iЙ—aЙ“ere maaЙ—a."
  20,23,"Men hollii ma Й—ii maandeeji Й—iЙ—i fii yo Men holle -an Muusaa- immorde e Aayeeje Amen MawЙ—e tinndinЙ—e Й—en e KattanЙ—e Amen, e wonndema kadi an ko o NulaaЙ—o immorde ka Alla."
  20,24,"Yahu -an Muusaa- ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o yawtii keerol ngol e keeferaaku ngun e sanndalЙ—anagol Alla."
  20,25,"Muusaa (yo o his) maaki: "Jooma, yaajinanam Й“ernde am nden; fii yo mi waawu ronnditaade larraaji(lorooji) Й—in."
  20,26,"Newinanaa mi fiyaake am on."
  20,27,"Wawnaa lam yewtugol yewtere laaЙ“unde."
  20,28,"Fii yo Й“a faamu haala am kan si Nulal am ngal yottike e maЙ“Й“e."
  20,29,"WaЙ—anaa mi walloowo jeyaaЙ—o ka Й“eynguure am o walla lam e fiyakuuji am."
  20,30,"Haaruuna geЙ—al Imraana ko musiЙ—Й—o am."
  20,31,"Semmbiniraa mo keeci am."
  20,32,"WaЙ—u mo kafidaaЙ—o e am e nder Nulal ngal."
  20,33,"Fii yo men Senine Seninaali heewuЙ—i."
  20,34,"Men jaЕ‹toMaa jaЕ‹ta heewuЙ—o."
  20,35,"Pellet, An A Laatike HumpitiiЙ—o fii amen, huunde suuЙ—anaaki Ma e fiyaake amen."
  20,36,"Alla Daali: "GomЙ—ii Men okkii ma ko Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—aa kon an Muusaa"."
  20,37,"GomЙ—ii Men Neeminiino e maaЙ—a e laawol goo."